# Backend: Google Sheets (no API key, no secrets).
# The site reads the PUBLIC (view-only) Google Sheet "Dixon Hall — Website"
# (tabs: Songs, Shows) via its gviz JSON. The sheet id is non-secret and is
# hardcoded in site/api/content.js.
#
# Nothing is required here. You may OPTIONALLY override the sheet id per
# environment (e.g. a staging copy) instead of editing the code:
# SHEET_ID=15GA2gv4DY5XhEJtmtUbAK-VL8ZVCrjv3q6XV6Ngwwts
